    "RC-D-consolidation": {
      "issue": 1274,
      "scope": "claim-key returns __unresolved__/__unknown__ singletons -> zero multi-source baskets. Loci: src/polaris_graph/synthesis/claim_graph.py:508 build_merge_key (returns at :545/:550), src/polaris_graph/synthesis/finding_dedup.py:100 _finding_key. FIX per DECISION 3 (two-operation, fail-closed): Op-1 keep the hard SAFETY merge key UNTOUCHED; Op-2 SEPARATE additive corroboration layer (LLM frame-extractor RELATE-pattern + Qwen3-Embedding-8B+NLI surface-canon for CLUSTERING-only) -> corroboration_id+count+weights+support/contradict; THREE-STATE PRESENT/UNKNOWN->singleton/N-A-from-deterministic-schema; over-merge guard exact-or-singleton; enable+slate-pin PG_BASKET_CONSUME_FINDING_DEDUP. Behavioral: multi_origin_cluster_count>1 on a real corpus. Folds TI-07..11.",
      "TRACE_FINDING_2026_06_20": "§-1.4 trace COMPLETE. ROOT CHOKEPOINT = consolidation is NUMERIC-ONLY. credibility_pass.py:824 _regroup_graph_by_finding_dedup merges ONLY claims where kind=='numeric' (the docstring: 'Non-numeric (qualitative/raw) claims are intentionally NOT in this map -> keep their legacy singleton id'). finding_dedup.dedup_by_finding likewise clusters by extract_numeric_claims (clinical-pattern-tuned; returns NOTHING for non-clinical). So on a GENERAL/multilingual DRB-II report (mostly QUALITATIVE claims) ~every claim is a singleton -> _assemble_baskets gives each a 1-member basket -> zero corroborators surfaced -> the 7-of-790 narrow breadth. This is EXACTLY the §-1.3 mandate 'finding_dedup/fact_dedup must CONSOLIDATE QUALITATIVE claims too, never restrict to numeric-only'. Op-1 (numeric fail-closed key) STAYS untouched (arch002 contracts test_20/5/23, clinical over-merge lethal). Op-2 = NEW qualitative-corroboration step clustering qualitative singletons by semantic-same-claim (reuse retrieval/pooled_embedder.py + entailment_judge NLI already in pipeline), entailment-CONFIRM gate (exact-or-singleton over-merge guard), feeding the SAME merge mechanism so members share a basket -> surfaced by the existing generator/weighted_enrichment.py + provenance_generator _verified_corroborators_for_tokens. Replay substrate = outputs/audits/b1b10_redesign/replay_fixtures/drb_72_ai_labor/corpus_snapshot.json (a GENERAL/qualitative question). Behavioral assert: qualitative multi_origin_cluster_count>1.",
