      "venue_check": "local Windows box CAN complete full runs (clean_local/drb_75, iarch011_drb78_run5, 204 report.md total) -> NO VM migration needed; docling OCR was the specific new killer."
    },
    "transient_429": "first v2 launch (PID 1118) aborted at the pre-spend super-heavy preflight: credibility-judge probe got a transient OpenRouter 429 (canary calls succeeded $0.0001/$0.0008 -> glm-5.2 alive, key works). Correctly aborted BEFORE spend. AIMD back-off 60s -> relaunch cleared it.",
