      "C_finalize_real_writer": "wire the real per-basket production writer into verified-compose PRIMARY (biggest change; the abstractive writer #1282 is the intended one but gated/unproven live)."
    },
    "constraint": "do NOT relax PG_MIN_VERIFIED_SECTION_FRACTION=0.40 (operator-signoff-gated clinical-safety floor). Fix chokepoint A (make STORM sections verify), NOT the floor. faithfulness gate untouched in all options.",
    "validation_plan": "resume_from_corpus (skips 85min retrieval, rebuilds baskets, re-generates -- cheaper than full $8/2.5h run) to confirm STORM sections verify before the final fresh scoreable re-run.",
    "gh_issue": "#1287 created.",
    "decision_pending": "advisor reconcile on A vs B vs C (gates expensive re-run + reverts a feature)."
  },
  "P6_ROOTCAUSE_TRUE_reduce_filter_eats_verified_compose_0720": {
    "CORRECTED_ROOT_CAUSE": "NOT a broken writer (my A/B/C fork was WRONG, advisor caught it via the dropped=0 signature). TRUE bug: multi_section_generator.py:3991 `if distillate is not None: raw=filter_and_strip_reduce_markers(raw,distillate)`. In REDUCE mode (active this run, 254 distill_map refs) this filter DROPS every sentence lacking a [[finding:]] marker. verified-compose PRIMARY draft carries valid [#ev:] tokens but NO [[finding:]] markers -> ENTIRE draft eaten -> raw='' -> 0 verified, dropped=0 (NEVER reached strict_verify -- matches the signature exactly).",
    "OFFLINE_PROOF": "filter_and_strip_reduce_markers('AI exposure raises wage inequality. [#ev:ev_abc:0-30]', distillate) -> '' (EATEN). Confirmed.",
    "why_others_survived": "contract sections use _call_section -> REDUCE prose WITH [[finding:]] markers -> survive filter. Corroborated Weighted Findings appended at line 7195 OUTSIDE the section loop -> bypasses the 3991 filter -> 1300 verified.",
    "PR_C_does_not_exonerate": "PR-c asserts on _compose_section_per_basket RETURN value, never runs the 3991 filter / 3998 rewrite / 4002 verify tail. PR-c green is fully consistent with the tail eating the output.",
    "FIX": "tiny + BREADTH-PRESERVING (advisor): exempt the directly-[#ev:]-tokened drafts (the _evsr FIX-K branch line 3896 + the verified-compose PRIMARY branch line 3910) from filter_and_strip_reduce_markers. Set a flag `_draft_directly_tokened=True` in those branches; gate line 3991 `if distillate is not None and not _draft_directly_tokened:`. The directly-tokened draft already carries valid [#ev:] -> flows STRAIGHT to _rewrite_draft_with_spans + strict_verify (the tail the comment FALSELY claimed was unchanged). faithfulness gate UNTOUCHED. The writer + breadth feature were fine all along.",
    "validation": "fail-loud replay harness: verified-compose draft with distillate ACTIVE must survive to verified>0 (RED on current code = eaten to 0; GREEN after fix). Then resume_from_corpus / fresh re-run.",
    "supersedes": "P6_FIX_PROBE_prc_harness_passes_0713 fork (A/B/C all misframed as broken writer)."
  },
  "P6_TWO_BUGS_filter_and_orphan_0730": {
    "BUG1_FIXED_COMMITTED": "reduce-marker filter (line 3991) eats verified-compose [#ev:]-only drafts. FIXED commit f6916d2b (_draft_directly_tokened flag bypasses the filter for FIX-K + verified-compose branches). harness iarch_beatboth009 green (RED+GREEN), PR-c green. NECESSARY but NOT sufficient.",
    "BUG2_CONFIRMED_PENDING": "split_into_sentences ORPHANS the token in the verified-compose draft format 'X. [#ev:id:0-89]' (token AFTER terminal period). PROVEN offline: _compose_section_per_basket real draft -> production tail (_rewrite_draft_with_spans -> strict_verify) = kept=0 dropped=1 no_provenance_token. So EVEN WITH bug1 fixed, the 12 STORM sections would STILL gap_stub (orphaned) -> a re-run with only bug1 fixed WASTES $8/2.5h. The advisor's 'settle offline before re-run' caught this.",
    "why_findings_survived": "Corroborated Weighted Findings (1300 verified) uses the SECTION-level _build_verified_span_draft (FIX-K, line 3896) which emits an orphan-SAFE format. The BASKET-level producers build_short_member_sentence (verified_compose.py:191) + build_verified_span_draft (line 162) emit orphan-PRONE 'X. [#ev:]' -> verified-compose path zeroed.",
    "BUG2_FIX_DIRECTION": "emit token BEFORE the terminal period: 'X [#ev:id:0-89].' so split_into_sentences keeps the token attached. Localize to the BASKET-level producers build_short_member_sentence + build_verified_span_draft (verified_compose.py); DO NOT touch the section-level FIX-K (findings, already orphan-safe -- don't break 1300). Token OFFSETS unchanged (index into evidence text, not draft) -> faithfulness-neutral. Validate: the offline _compose_section_per_basket->production-tail test must flip to kept>0 + PR-c must stay green, BEFORE Codex-gate + re-run.",
    "next": "FRESH next turn (faithfulness-adjacent, do with care): read build_short_member_sentence + build_verified_span_draft, fix token-before-period, validate offline (compose->production-tail kept>0 + PR-c green + harness green), commit, Codex-gate both bugs, THEN fresh re-run."
  },
  "P6_BOTH_BUGS_FIXED_CODEX_GATING_0745": {
    "bug1": "FIXED+committed f6916d2b (reduce-filter bypass for directly-tokened drafts).",
    "bug2": "FIXED+committed eeb783c7 (token-before-period in build_short_member_sentence + build_verified_span_draft; offsets UNCHANGED, faithfulness identical).",
    "offline_validation": "DECISIVE: real _compose_section_per_basket -> production tail (_rewrite_draft_with_spans -> strict_verify) flipped kept 0 -> 1. iarch_beatboth009 end-to-end harness GREEN (RED filter-eats + GREEN verifies>0). PR-c GREEN. iarch_beatboth002 multicited GREEN on real corpus. All faithfulness-neutral.",
