>     # so the persisted, cited [7mdirect_quote[0m — and every [#ev:id:start-end] offset[0m
[7m[0m      # the generator later resolves against it — is computed on the de-hyphenated[0m
[7m[0m      # text. Newlines survive clean_fetch_body (it collapses only [ \t]{2,}), so the[0m
