[7m[0m      # DOI / license extraction) while a later chunk is real content, lead the quote with the FIRST[0m
>     # real-content chunk so a real-content span wins the [7mdirect_quote[0m over a furniture span. Every chunk[0m
[7m[0m      # is a verbatim substring of the de-hyphenated content, so re-leading is faithfulness-neutral and the[0m
