[7m[0m      # OFF or a non-furniture head (picker returns index 0) => chunks unchanged => byte-identical.[0m
[7m[0m      # P2b import hygiene: ``shell_detector`` is already imported at module load (top of file), and[0m
[7m[0m      # the env-gate is checked BEFORE the picker is invoked, so the DEFAULT (flag-OFF) path carries no[0m
[7m[0m      # new import/attribute/failure surface — only an env read + the len()>1 check, then it returns.[0m
[7m[0m      if len(chunks) > 1 and shell_detector.span_select_furniture_aware_enabled():[0m
[7m[0m          _idx, _ = shell_detector.select_real_content_span(chunks)[0m
[7m[0m          if _idx > 0:[0m
