>     hygiene: it removes only confirmed fetch [7mmetadata[0m / chrome, never assertional[0m
[7m[0m      prose; the strict_verify / NLI / 4-role / span-grounding gates keep full[0m
[7m[0m      strictness on everything that remains.[0m
