[7m[0m  def _crawl4ai_backed_off_cooldown(generation: int) -> float:[0m
[7m[0m      """I-fetch-005 (#1344) FIX 1: exponential-backoff cooldown for the crawl4ai breaker.[0m
[7m[0m  [0m
[7m[0m      generation 1 -> BASE, 2 -> BASE*BACKOFF, 3 -> BASE*BACKOFF^2, ... capped at MAX_COOLDOWN.[0m
[7m[0m      A genuinely-dead browser (missing OS libs on the box) therefore backs OFF geometrically[0m
[7m[0m      instead of being re-probed every BASE seconds forever; a transient hiccup still recovers[0m
[7m[0m      at BASE (the generation resets to 0 on the first successful probe). BACKOFF<=1 =>[0m
[7m[0m      constant BASE cooldown (legacy shape)."""[0m
