671	
672	      1. TOC-shaped: at least ``PG_FRONT_MATTER_TOC_LINE_MIN`` (default 8) dot-leader
673	         runs (``...`` before a page number). A real article head / reference list
674	         carries ZERO (calibrated on the real banked drb_78 corpus: genuine TOC heads
675	         carry 13–14, every real article head carries 0).
676	      2. ISSN masthead: an ``ISSN dddd-dddd`` marker AND contents/editorial-board vocab
677	         co-occur (both required — an incidental "contents" mention or a lone ISSN
678	         citation in real prose trips neither). Covers the Cyrillic dgpu-class masthead
679	         (``СОДЕРЖАНИЕ`` / ``РЕДАКЦИОННАЯ КОЛЛЕГИЯ`` + ISSN).
680	
681	    NEVER a DROP: a ``True`` verdict marks the SPAN ``wrong_content_span`` so the caller
